  "body": "### Description\r\nWhen a vc is configured with multiple beacon node endpoints and the primary beacon node is online but syncing, the vc fails to produce sync committee messages when it should have been able to via the fallback:\r\n\r\n```\r\n{\"@timestamp\":\"2022-10-26T20:15:16,005\",\"level\":\"WARN\",\"thread\":\"ValidatorTimingChannel-1\",\"class\":\"teku-validator-log\",\"message\":\"Validator   *** Skipped producing sync_signature while node is syncing  Count: 1, Slot: 4192276\",\"throwable\":\"\"}\r\n```\r\n\r\nIt is producing attestations and aggregates correctly.",
